title: Muangkan United F.C.
text:
Muangkan United Football Club (<a href="Thai%20alphabet">Thai</a> สโมสรฟุตบอลเมืองกาญจน์ ยูไนเต็ด) is a Thai professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Kanchanaburi%20Province">Kanchanaburi Province</a>. The club is currently playing in the <a href="Thai%20League%202">Thai League 2</a>.
History.
In 2009 Muangkan United Football Club is formed as Muangkan Football Club, nicknamed "The Bats". Home games to be played at <a href="Kanchanaburi%20Province%20Stadium">Kanchanaburi Province Stadium</a>. In 2010 the club join the professional league that was <a href="2010%20Regional%20League%20Division%202%20Central%20%26amp%3B%20Eastern%20Region">2010 Regional League Division 2 Central & Eastern Region</a>.
